OL,3,CHistoric tramtown closed until further
OL,4,Cnotice after electrical fault
OL,6,FA historic visitor attraction has been
OL,7,Fforced to close until further notice
OL,8,Fdue to an issue with an electrical
OL,9,Fcable.
OL,11,FConcerns have been raised that there
OL,12,Fis no confirmed timescale for the
OL,13,Frepair of Blackpool Tramtown, and no
OL,14,Fcertainty that the issue can be fixed.
OL,16,FSeveral of the heritage trams are
OL,17,Fnormally kept in the historic
OL,18,Fworkshop, along with all of the
OL,19,Fmachinery that is needed for their
OL,20,Fmaintenance.
