OL,6,FPaul Galley, Project Manager at
OL,7,FBlackpool Tramtown, said the closure
OL,8,Fis deeply affecting those who have
OL,9,Fdedicated years to preserving
OL,10,FBlackpool's tram heritage.
OL,12,FCllr Galley - also the leader of
OL,13,FBlackpool Council's Conservative
OL,14,Fopposition - said: "The volunteers and
OL,15,Fsupporters of Tramtown are hurting
OL,16,Fright now.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
