OL,6,FHe added that he had asked Cllr Lynn
OL,7,FWilliams, Leader of Blackpool Council,
OL,8,Fto come and meet him and the
OL,9,Fvolunteers directly, to hear first-
OL,10,Fhand how they are being affected.
OL,12,FCllr Galley said. "Decisions about
OL,13,FTramtown should be based on informed
OL,14,Funderstanding, not on advice from
OL,15,Fthose with another agenda ` one that
OL,16,Fis focused on demolishing the tram
OL,17,Fworkshops and leaving historic trams
OL,18,Fto rot in a condemned tramshed with
OL,19,Fvague promises of future funding.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
