OL,6,F"In the last three years the tramshed
OL,7,Fhas been condemned, the engineers have
OL,8,Fall been made redundant, the volunteer
OL,9,Fdrivers and conductors have been
OL,10,Freleased, and now Tramtown is closed.
OL,12,F"This is a disaster for Blackpool and
OL,13,Fits unique cultural history. Despite
OL,14,Fassurances that a funding bid is being
OL,15,Fprepared, volunteers have not been
OL,16,Fengaged or consulted on its contents."
OL,26,@xD@fOU
