OL,6,F"The Council say they are working on a
OL,7,Ffunding bid, yet they will not engage
OL,8,Fwith the very people who have done the
OL,9,Fwork, built the case by turning up in
OL,10,Fall weathers, and kept Tramtown alive.
OL,12,F"What is the plan, and why are the
OL,13,Fvolunteers being excluded?"
OL,15,FCllr Lynn Williams, the Leader of
OL,16,FBlackpool Council, says a final
OL,17,Fdecision has not been made on whether
OL,18,FTramtown's engineering shed, which is
OL,19,Fseparate from the building which
OL,20,Fhouses the trams, will be demolished.
