OL,6,FShe said at last week's Full Council
OL,7,Fmeeting that it would cost millions of
OL,8,Fpounds to properly renovate the site.
OL,10,FHowever, she said she was committed to
OL,11,Fshort term and long term plans for the
OL,12,Ffacility.
OL,14,FCllr Galley added: "It is most
OL,15,Fimportant that we focus on the way
OL,16,Fforward and deliver a sustainable
OL,17,Ffuture for Tram Town."
